		   "body" : "See the example:\r\n\r\n```exp(0) - log(e) + sqrt(9) / tan(45Â°)``` \r\n\r\nThe result should be 1 - 1 + 3 / 1 = 3\r\n\r\nInstead [no answer is returned](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=exp(0)+-+log(e)+ 0+sqrt(9)+0.000000+tan(45Â°))\r\n\r\nThe goody lacks of support to the following notations:\r\n\r\n* [```exp(x)```](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=exp                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          %29) ([```e^x```](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=e^3) is already supported) \r\n* [```TrigonometricalFunction(xÂ°)```](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=sin%2845Â°%29) ([support to radians]((https://duckduckgo.com/?q=sin                      7598b0i%29)) is already in the code)\r\n* [```atan(x)```](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=atan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        %29) / [```arctan(x)```](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=arctan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        %29) (same with asin/arcsin and acos/arccos)\r\n* [```HyperbolicTrigonometricalFunction(x)```](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=sinh                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       %29) (```sinh```/```sh```, ```cosh```/```ch```, ```tanh```/```th```, ```arcsinh```/```asinh```, ```arccosh```/```acosh``` and ```arctanh```/```atanh```)\r\n\r\n----\r\n\r\nIA Page: http://duck.co/ia/view/calculator",
