		   "body" : "Adds more tests to the `CheatSheets` Controller.\r\n\r\nAlso fixes #1844 and cleans up some cheat sheets that were violating tests.\r\n\r\n### Tests\r\n\r\n* ~~**Warning** if tabs are used for indenting.~~\r\n* ~~**Warning** if an indent that is not a multiple of 4 is used.~~\r\n* ~~**Warning** if trailing white-space is detected.~~\r\n* **Critical** if an alias is used that duplicates the cheat sheet name.\r\n* **Critical** if an alias is used that contains uppercase characters.\r\n* **Critical** if the ID does not follow the expected naming conventions.\r\n* **Critical** if the file name does not follow the expected naming conventions.\r\n* **Critical** if no `template_type` is specified.\r\n* **Dies** if an alias is used that is the name of another cheat sheet.\r\n* **Dies** if an alias is used that is already in use.\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n[IA Page](https://duck.co/ia/view/cheat_sheets)",
